            "notes": "The key strategy of this Aggro Cosmic Spider-Man deck is to overwhelm the opponent with a mix of powerful creatures, versatile spells, and efficient removal. By utilizing a combination of quick creatures like Aang, Swift Savior and board control cards like Aragorn, King of Gondor, the deck aims to pressure the opponent early while disrupting their game plan. With a range of counterspells like Force Spike and Remand, along with removal spells such as Dismember and Swords to Plowshares, the deck can handle a variety of threats. Additionally, the deck includes powerful finishers like Omnath, Locus of Creation and Voice of Victory to seal the game once the opponent is on the back foot."
